Comment: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:21.50,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:81509,81509}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99442,101242}Just a bit longer! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108276,110076}See you at the bottom, crybabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110276,112009}Who does she think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112009,115076}I'm sick of her captainship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115742,117876}This girl does nothing\Nbut sows discord in our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117876,121242}Let's take different route today, too.\NHow about the hills outside the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.24,0:02:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121242,123509}Good idea. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131176,132409}These hills?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132409,134042}How far do they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134042,136376}It's said that the teams\Nwho can conquer these hills
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136376,139409}have a bright future\Nawaiting them wherever they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139409,143909}So it's not just us who poured buckets\Nof sweat on this hellish road?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144409,145676}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145676,148176}Somehow that doesn't comfort me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154209,155609}What a nice change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155609,158576}I'm starting to see\Nthe good sides of these hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191142,193542}We just keep running and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193542,195209}I'd like to play already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195209,197976}I'd like to practice\Nmy storytelling, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198142,201976}What are you talking about?\NStamina is essential, without it there's no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202276,205476}We run to train our legs and\Nlater be able to jump well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205642,209476}Changing the subject,\Ndo you smell some food, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210276,211676}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218109,219942}Hey, it's the boys\Nfrom the jūdō club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223809,226309}Oh, you're here.\NThanks, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226576,229542}Alright, guys.\NThis food is from our sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229542,232176}I expect these plates\Nto be licked clean, understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232176,233476}Sure thing, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233476,235476}Boy, this is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238542,240942}They have their own sponsors?\NMust be nice…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240942,245542}Yes, but their club has special circumstances.\NArashi-kun's father is very respected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247609,252042}How about our club\Nlooked for some sponsors, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252042,253342}Great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253342,254376}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255609,258876}Our club has only six people,\Nand you already think about the sponsors?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265342,266609}Hijiri-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267642,268909}Come here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270076,272509}Soon we'll be allocating\Nthe budget for this semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272509,275609}Among other things, we'll decide\Nhow much each club will get.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275609,277909}Could you fill out the application?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277909,279509}No problem.\NWe'll deliver it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279509,280976}Thanks. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284209,287176}Can I ask you, our captain,\Nto fill out this application?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287176,291642}Don't make me laugh. You know best\Nthat I'm a captain just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291642,293676}Why don't you fill\Nthat paperwork by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294776,297276}Yukari, come on, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297276,298276}Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298276,300176}We'll be back soon.\NKeep practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300176,304909}Hey, I have experience as a manager.\NMaybe I could do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304909,309276}Don't get me wrong, but here you are\None of the players, not a manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309276,310242}Go back to exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310242,311776}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312776,316209}I don't think we can expect\Ntoo much money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316209,320509}The committee will be definitely looking\Nat the achievements from recent years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320509,325309}Our club has no recent achievements\Nand it's been closed for the last six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325309,327442}Despite that,\Nwe've got to try, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329742,332042}– Hey, Kyōsuke, hurry up.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334242,340076}Hey, we finally have the chance to practice some\Nreceptions instead of running around as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340076,341076}I'm all for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341376,344076}I don't think they're going to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344076,347942}This is also an important part of training.\NIt'll be okay. Come on, let's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347942,350209}– I'll serve.\N– Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350209,352576}All right, I'll be on defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354076,355509}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355509,356842}Yes, bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367509,369942}I'm sorry, could you pass it to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373209,374742}Throw it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374742,376742}Yes, I was just about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384276,387409}Looks like you'll have\Nto buy a new net.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387409,389542}I hope you have\Nenough budget for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391776,393242}What are we going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393242,394409}I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395942,397176}Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397176,400176}Leave it to me.\NI'll go talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402242,403609}Ichijō-san said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403609,406876}Yes. I'm afraid\Nit won't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428009,429776}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432209,435209}{\i1}Awesome. What precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435209,437876}{\i1}Just like I thought,\NIchijō-san must've played before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437876,440376}Which one of you\Nhit me in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440376,442176}Where are you going?\NIchijō, was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444976,446576}{\i1}Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446576,449042}Perfect. Finally we can settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449642,450909}It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452176,455209}Wha… What?\NSo it was you, Hijiri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455209,458442}Ah, everything's cool.\NIt doesn't even hurt that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458442,459842}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459842,461342}There's nothing to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461342,465876}It's just that the window was opened so slightly,\Nthat I thought you did it on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465876,468542}But it was only you, Hijiri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469409,474042}I don't think you can reach there from where\NHijiri-san stands without breaking the windows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474409,477042}What… What are you saying?\NThen who threw this ball?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477442,478742}It was me, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478742,481076}Is that so?\NWhy don't you try again, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483909,487742}If it really was you,\Nprove it and do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487742,488942}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488942,490309}Throw me the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490309,492409}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492409,495042}I'll be happy to see it again,\Nthis time from the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495042,496776}Close the window as it was then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498642,500276}A bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500576,503276}What? More?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506876,509776}Mimi, don't fool around.\NIf we break the windows, it'll be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511142,512309}Show me what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520942,522676}She did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523242,525909}Well, well!\NWe have a little champion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525909,527876}I'm throwing it back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529242,531409}Close the window even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531409,534076}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535176,537076}Watch close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537542,540042}Ichijō-kun, give me that ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540042,541276}Professor…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542976,545242}Hey, boys!\NClose that window altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545442,547542}And there you have it, show's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547542,549742}It was just about to get good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550076,553776}I hope you don't think that volleyball\Nis about showing off such cheap tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553776,555542}Anyway, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558876,560542}Where are you pointing, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566476,567342}No, it's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577976,579809}Ouch! God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588776,593342}Professor, if you're so good,\Nwhy have you been hiding it so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593676,596109}I wasn't really hiding anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:10:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596109,600609}Professor was a very good player. In college,\Nhe played for the Japanese national team.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600609,602676}How do you know all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602676,606076}Because he was a volleyball coach\Nat the school I used to go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608176,612342}Professor, we have a request.\NPlease become our coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612342,614576}We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619776,622976}I'd love to do it, but you see,\Nyou can't call yourself a team yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622976,625542}When you unite,\NI'll come to you myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625542,627409}For now, you still have\Nto work on yourselves.
Comment: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:44.07,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:644076,644076}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651276,654776}Hijiri-kun, tomorrow\Nis the next budget meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.77,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654776,657742}Tell your captain that\Nshe must be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.74,0:10:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657742,658876}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658876,660876}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661509,665709}Mimi, you're not really going\Nto ask her, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666709,668709}I have no choice.\NShe's our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.00,0:11:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670009,673876}Ichijō-san, you heard him, right?\NWould you go to this meeting for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673876,675942}I don't want to go to any meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:676442,680142}So you won't mind Mimi\Ngoing there on your behalf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680142,681442}Be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682542,684376}We'd better count\Neverything again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685509,688576}I'm afraid that it won't be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688576,690742}Everyone at school\Nknows perfectly well
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690742,694242}that most of the budget will go\Nto our basketball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694242,695142}See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695142,696176}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696176,696976}Yukari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703976,705109}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705109,706576}Here's a little something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706576,710342}We should have at least two uniforms per person,\None for training and one for games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710342,713842}Yes, we also need to think\Nabout running tracksuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713842,717342}Now we use the same ones\Nwe use for physical education classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:12:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717542,721142}Yes. I'd also like to order\Na new net and balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721142,723876}Oh, gosh. My head hurts\Nfrom all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723876,727176}Now you understand,\Nchild, why I'm always saying
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727176,729576}that expenditure planning\Nmakes me lose weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729576,731642}Yeah, I get it, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731642,735609}But it's probably nothing serious, ma'am,\Nbecause you're not exactly skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735609,739909}You'd better watch your tongue, young lady,\Nor else you won't get these cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739909,743609}Ah, I'm sorry, I'm sorry.\NIt was just a slip of the tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.37,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:749342,752376}Student Council budget meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756376,758742}Good morning, Hijiri-san.\NDo you need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758742,760676}This is where the\Nbudget meeting is held, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760676,761742}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761742,763476}Alright, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763476,766842}The only people authorized\Nto participate in the budget meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766842,771509}are the members of the Student Council,\Nand club chairmen or captains.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:772176,773976}But I represent…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773976,775509}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775509,777842}Is the chairman there?\NCould he come here for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778442,779809}Yes? How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779809,783476}Only club chairmen can attend\Nthe budget meeting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783476,785076}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785076,788542}But wait, if the chairman can't\Njoin for some important reasons…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788542,793242}Of course, but like you said, it must be\Nan important reason, such as illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793242,796609}And I've seen your captain\Ntoday at school, safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798776,800709}Hijiri-kun, rules are rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800709,802942}I'm afraid Ichijō-san\Nmust come here in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811176,813709}That's why we're forced\Nto ask you to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813709,815176}It's enough if I just\Nshow up there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815176,816876}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816876,819609}You'll need to negotiate with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819609,822476}This is the copy of our requests.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822476,827342}They'll try to downplay them, because\Nwe didn't have any achievements last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827342,832809}So we're asking initially for 165,000 yen,\Nbut if you manage to get 100,000, it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833276,834909}I've got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837376,839776}I'm not sure\Nif she really does, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841776,844242}Ichijō-san has already shown\Nthat she can get what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844242,847242}I don't know. Somehow,\NI have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847809,851242}Then we have the Women's Volleyball Club.\NAs probably everyone knows…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851242,853276}I think we can just skip over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853276,857776}You're terrible. Let's at least\Ngive them enough for the laces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860242,864709}I'm asking the club captain to speak up. You've\Nentered in the form the sum of 165,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864709,867609}Can you please explain\Nwhat you plan to spend it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867609,869242}I don't really know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870409,872376}And she's supposed\Nto be their captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873676,875942}60,000 yen should be\Nenough for their club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875942,879442}If you want more money,\Ngo find yourself a sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:879776,882442}Who would want\Nto finance a ghost team?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882742,886442}In my opinion, 60,000\Nis more than they deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890009,892276}Mimi! I've got some intel\Nfrom the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892276,893742}Have they approved\Nthe budget yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893742,895809}The look on your face\Nsays it didn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895809,899209}That's an understatement. Our budget\Nfor the whole year is 60,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899209,901776}60,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910076,911209}Ichijō-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912076,912942}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912942,915709}For this sum we won't be able\Nto afford even uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916409,917742}What of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918109,920409}You're the captain\Nof this club, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920409,922409}How could you let this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922409,923709}Yukari!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923709,926942}They told that if it's not enough,\Nwe should find ourselves a sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926942,928909}A sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930142,932042}I'm sorry, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935742,941042}I live on the hills and often see you\Ngirls running near our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941309,944342}Ah, you're the one who lives in that house\Nwith beautiful flowers, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944576,950809}Yes. However, I haven't seen you for a few days\Nand I was wondering if everything was all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950809,955376}We had a budget meeting and then other things,\Nso we haven't really had any time to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955376,961909}I understand. By the way, I have a sick daughter\Nwho has been bedridden since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961909,968909}She is a great fan of volleyball\Nand always looks forward to your visits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968909,972909}However, she hasn't seen you lately\Nand she's been missing you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972909,975709}I'm here with\Na huge request in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975709,980609}If this is not a problem for you, maybe you\Ncould go jogging in our area again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980609,984642}No problem.\NYour visit made us very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006276,1007342}They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013209,1015542}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015809,1019509}Good morning, Kanako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022376,1024509}I hope you'll get better soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.37,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026376,1030676}If you're bored,\Nyou can listen to my stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030676,1033609}Stop it, unless you\Nwant her to get worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033609,1035342}How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035342,1036842}See you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037076,1038576}I have a question…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038576,1039609}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039609,1042509}Why is each of you wearing\Na different uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048976,1050809}You see, that's because…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051442,1057276}We have our uniforms from the last year,\Nbut the freshmen didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057276,1060309}I can't wait to see you\Nin new uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060976,1062909}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074276,1077276}One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084176,1089042}How does the basketball club afford\Nnew outfits for the whole team?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089042,1091842}They just have good sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.84,0:18:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091842,1096542}Maybe we will also find someone\Nwho would be ready to finance us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097209,1101542}If we want to have decent clothes,\Nwe will have to sew them ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101542,1105909}In fact, many clubs do that.\NIf you want it, you can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105909,1111809}To be honest, I don't feel like playing,\Nat least not until we have proper uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.80,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111809,1116076}Okay. Raise your hand if you agree\Nwe could sew the costumes by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116076,1117376}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119409,1122542}Maybe it'd be better\Nto disband the club, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132742,1135442}– Good morning.\N– Good morning, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135442,1137442}I'm glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138009,1139742}You can go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139742,1142776}She wouldn't listen to me.\NShe said she just had to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142776,1145942}To think that once I had\Nto force her to take walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145942,1148942}{\i1}This girl is supporting us so much and\Nhere we're talking about closing the club…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149276,1151209}Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155842,1158109}With this, you'll be able\Nto afford new uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160442,1164309}There is probably no more\Nthan 1,000 yen inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164309,1169442}However, my daughter kept insisting\Nthat she wanted to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169442,1176742}We hope that you'll be able to quickly\Nraise the funds for the new uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176742,1179076}My daughter would love\Nto see you in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180442,1182442}Here. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183776,1185742}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185742,1189576}You see?\NWe have our sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189576,1192942}She is just a little girl,\Nbut she supports us with all her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194776,1196909}I'm sorry, Kanako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196909,1200476}We can't accept\Nyour beautiful gift yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200476,1204776}Rather of focusing on what really matters,\Nwe were concerned with uniforms and budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204776,1209242}Even the world's largest budget is useless\Nif there's no team to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209676,1215242}I promise you that one day you will see\Nall of us in beautiful new uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215876,1218676}Yes. But first,\Nwe must work for this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218676,1219742}I'm all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219742,1220642}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220642,1221742}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221742,1223642}Let's give it our best, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223642,1224776}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224776,1226442}Are you with us, Ichijō-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242742,1243776}Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244009,1245509}Ichijō-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246376,1247642}Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248076,1249642}Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254276,1257176}Young lady, I'd like\Nto express my gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257176,1259709}as the coach of the Tachibana\NHigh School Volleyball Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259709,1261409}As the coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261742,1263409}As the coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263809,1265676}As the coach…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267809,1274809}Your support for their team turned out\Nto be more valuable than any funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274809,1276076}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285576,1288176}{\i1}Thanks to the warm support\Nof a single little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288176,1293276}{\i1}the team united and Daisuke\Nagreed to become their coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.27,0:21:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293276,1299542}{\i1}However, this event was only\Nthe beginning of a long, long way.
Comment: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:47.74,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1307742,1307742}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310909,1313476}A match?\NYou've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313476,1316542}So what if we lose? We should have fun\Nfirst and foremost, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:22:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1316542,1320942}No. If we play, we must win.\NThat's the essence of sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320942,1325409}A match lets us assess our skills\Nand tells us how much we need to improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325409,1330276}Our first opponent will be\Na team of adult fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331076,1333142}In the next episode of\N"Attack on Tomorrow":
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333142,1335709}"A Serve at the Seaside".\NSee you soon!
